Dataset Attributions:

This project uses the following datasets under their respective licenses:

1. RAVDESS (Ryerson Audio-Visual Database of Emotional Speech and Song)
   - License: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License
   - Citation: Livingstone SR, Russo FA (2018) The Ryerson Audio-Visual Database of 
     Emotional Speech and Song (RAVDESS): A dynamic, multimodal set of facial and 
     vocal expressions in North American English. PLoS ONE 13(5): e0196391. 
     https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0196391

2. CREMA-D (Crowd-sourced Emotional Multimodal Actors Dataset)
   - License: Open access dataset
   - Citation: Cao, H., Cooper, D. G., Keutmann, M. K., Gur, R. C., Nenkova, A., 
     & Verma, R. (2014). CREMA-D: Crowd-sourced emotional multimodal actors dataset. 
     IEEE transactions on affective computing, 5(4), 377-390.

3. TESS (Toronto Emotional Speech Set)
   - License: Open access dataset
   - Citation: Dupuis, K., & Pichora-Fuller, M. K. (2010). Toronto emotional speech 
     set (TESS). University of Toronto, Psychology Department.

Users of this software must comply with the respective dataset licenses when using 
the provided datasets or any derivatives thereof.
